response.overview: Two filmmakers and childhood best friends fresh off of the success of their first indie film, decide to make the move to Los Angeles in the hopes of finding new success. Soon after, they are invited to an exclusive party in the Hollywood Hills by a powerful studio executive and they realize that this town is not all that they thought it was.
